    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<h2>Ailen Moraven — Tamsin's Daughter</h2>\n<p><em>Tamsin Moraven's daughter, in her twenties, has been living quietly in Hardby since her mother's disappearance. Watchful, traveled, cautious. The party may meet her early in Phase 3 and use her safe-house if they earn her trust.</em></p>\n<h3>Combat behavior</h3>\n<p>Capable but reluctant. Carries a small dagger and knows how to use it. Will fight in defense of her mother or of her household.</p>\n<h3>Statblock summary (CR 1/8, PB +2)</h3>\n<p>AC 12 · HP 22 (4d8+4) · Speed 30 ft. · Init +2 · Passive Perception 13</p>\n<p>STR 11 · DEX 14 · CON 12 · INT 13 · WIS 14 · CHA 13. Skills: Insight +4, Perception +4, Stealth +4, Survival +4.</p>\n<p>Dagger +4 melee, 1d4+2 piercing. Languages: Common, Old Aerdi.</p>\n<h3>Source</h3>\n<p><em>Blooming Rot, Part 2 — Phase 3.</em> See <em>Hardby NPCs → Ailen Moraven — Tamsin's Daughter</em> for full profile.</p>",
        "public": ""
      },
